    "story_name": "圣都格拉姆斯 第17章 5-6 野心",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "古拉特暗藏对格拉姆斯教皇之位的野心，\\n命令哈尔前去夺取晓之圣片。\\n然而，哈尔假意效忠古拉特，\\n实则企图独吞圣片，\\n带着志在必得的笑容向北进发。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "格拉姆斯教皇厅",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "（伊莉雅教会教皇的宝座……\\n是统领这座城市，不，是统领\\n北格拉斯迪亚的最高权力者的宝座。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "（我这个曾经\\n吃了上顿没下顿的贫民之子，\\n如今正试图夺取那至尊之座。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "（还差一点，\\n终有一天我定要……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "终有一天……\\n定要自己坐上那宝座——\\n都写在您脸上了呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "是哈尔啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "古拉特大人，久违了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "开玩笑也要适度。\\n这里可是神圣的\\n教皇陛下的宝座……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "呵呵，您放心吧。\\n我已经屏退左右了，\\n没有人会偷听。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "煽动保守派和炼狱派对立\\n以分裂南格拉斯迪亚的教会……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "甚至在南格拉斯迪亚民间\\n撒下叛乱的火种以削弱王室。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "古拉特大人的计划\\n全都顺利地进行着。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "这一切都是为了\\n闪耀的格拉姆斯\\n能拥有长期稳定的发展。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "是呢，我当然知道。\\n一切都是为了格拉姆斯，\\n为了伟大的伊莉雅教。呵呵……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "哈尔……你来到这里\\n应该不只是为了说胡话吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "不，我是前来报告即将出发的。\\n请原谅我迟迟未能进入正题。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "我一定带回您心心念念的\\n晓之圣片，献至尊前。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "我认可你平日的功劳……\\n这回也很看好你。\\n需要哪些人或物，尽管用就是。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "幸得枢机主教阁下此言，\\n我深感荣幸。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "那么，我就此告辞。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "哼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "（阳奉阴违这个词简直就是\\n为哈尔那家伙存在的。\\n真是个恶魔般的男人。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "（城府太深让人看不透，\\n要驯服他果然还是难了些。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "（不过，这次的任务\\n只有他这样的人胜任\\n也是事实……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "（万一他能带回圣片……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120194_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "古拉特",
            "context": "（那宝座就终于\\n轮到我……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "无人不求，无人不寻，\\n至高无上的圣片……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "“我自己”没有理由\\n不想要呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "差不多该出发了。\\n前往众人聚集的精灵之域……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "让我也加入争夺战吧，\\n呵呵……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}